      "acceptanceCriteria": "SQA level 2 requires documented version control and regression test suite covering primary load paths. Achieved level 3 additionally includes formal change-control procedures and independent code review records.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1 is a commercially validated FEA solver subject to the vendor's ISO 9001 quality management system. The FDA in-house Python post-processing scripts are maintained under Git version control with a documented regression test suite. Independent code review was performed by a second analyst prior to submission. Achieved level 3 exceeds the required level 2 for medium model risk."
